Program: Discovery
Title: Fuelling the Future - back to basics
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrz3y
Last Broadcast Date: 03 March 2006
In a series on the future of energy, could ancient power sources plug the energy gap? Richard Black examines some of mankinds oldest sources of power and heat, water, sun and fire, and looks at how the application of modern science could harness them for future energy.